Time to prove it! Come to L306.]

201
00:14:20,793 --> 00:14:24,663
Jeez. That's it? No context?

202
00:14:26,203 --> 00:14:30,121
No explanations, and so abrupt.

203
00:14:31,433 --> 00:14:33,433
