215
00:16:14,432 --> 00:16:17,743
Do you want me to go?

216
00:16:17,743 --> 00:16:20,070
Oh, thank you.

217
00:16:21,421 --> 00:16:23,719
I mean... just like that?

218
00:16:24,882 --> 00:16:26,554
